{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#Informal.informalLemmaDecl\"><span class=\"name\">Informal</span>.<span class=\"name\">informalLemmaDecl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A placeholder for lemmas to be formalized in the future. Docstrings of informal lemmas\nshould outline its mathematical or physical content and specify useful references. Use the attribute\n`note_attr_informal` from `PhysLean.Meta.Notes.Basic` to mark the informal definition as a note.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#Informal.informalLemmaDecl","kind":"def","line":61,"name":"Informal.informalLemmaDecl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L61-L63"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#Informal.informalDefinitionDecl\"><span class=\"name\">Informal</span>.<span class=\"name\">informalDefinitionDecl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A placeholder for definitions to be formalized in the future. Docstrings of informal definitions\nshould outline its mathematical or physical content and specify useful references. Use the attribute\n`note_attr_informal` from `PhysLean.Meta.Notes.Basic` to mark the informal definition as a note.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#Informal.informalDefinitionDecl","kind":"def","line":53,"name":"Informal.informalDefinitionDecl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L53-L55"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<s